headline.main: Graham Says He Doesn't Know What GOP Health Care Plan Is Yet
headline.print_headline: Graham Says He Doesn't Know What GOP Health Care Plan Is Yet

lead_paragraph: U.S. Sen. Lindsey Graham told a rowdy town hall in South Carolina that health care is going to change in the United States. Just don't ask him for details.
